sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as Claude Code Agent
    participant Pup as Puppeteer
    participant App as Next.js App
    participant DOM as DOM / Viewport

    Note over Agent,DOM: Validation loop for each of 21 screens

    Agent->>Pup: Launch browser (1920x1080)
    activate Pup

    loop For each screen (21 total)
        Agent->>Pup: Navigate to route
        Pup->>App: GET /screen-path
        App-->>Pup: Rendered page
        Pup->>DOM: Wait for selector (content loaded)
        DOM-->>Pup: Element visible

        Pup->>DOM: Take full-page screenshot
        DOM-->>Pup: PNG capture

        Pup->>DOM: Evaluate DOM structure
        Note right of DOM: Query headings, buttons,<br/>cards, forms, nav items

        DOM-->>Pup: Element counts & text content
        Pup-->>Agent: Assertion results

        alt All assertions pass
            Agent->>Agent: Mark screen PASS
        else Assertion failure
            Agent->>Agent: Log failure details
            Agent->>Agent: Fix component code
            Agent->>Pup: Re-navigate & re-validate
        end

        opt Interactive elements present
            Pup->>DOM: Click buttons / fill forms
            DOM-->>Pup: State change response
            Pup->>DOM: Screenshot post-interaction
            DOM-->>Pup: Updated capture
            Pup-->>Agent: Interaction results
        end
    end

    Agent->>Agent: Compile validation report
    Note over Agent: 107 total actions across 21 screens

    deactivate Pup
